skal st\u00e5 i en krig, blir \u00abEn dag uten krig\u00bb noe mer enn vakker julefortelling og en illustrert klassiker; nemlig en habil grinefilm med budskap og brodd."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|film"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "kultur|film|filmanmeldelser"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "b633a3ee305d57efea38a0a401fbacfe054504ff2881b50999a12e9058de37d9"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-12-03T20:34:05.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "FILM: Ber\u00f8mt gammel krigslegende som velment, ubehagelig aktuell historie om menneskelighet i ulvetider."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1153239.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/endagutenkrig800"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/7b95c73f82a393c4523fa2ae59d0e80d364ba215.jpg?590cfa94"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Jul i skyttergrava -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "7b95c73f82a393c4523fa2ae59d0e80d364ba215"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["trondheim kino", "kino", "dvd", "video", "kosmorama", "filmfestivaler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "trondheim kino,kino,dvd,video,kosmorama,filmfestivaler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["kultur", "filmanmeldelser", "film"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["ubehagelig aktuell", "dag", "film", "umenneskelig", "historie", "krig"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "pipes of peace"}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "frankrike"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["christian carions", "paul mccartneys"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["kultur/film/filmanmeldelser", "kultur", "kultur/film"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa